### Movielandia API — Movie Endpoints
### Requires VS Code REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)
### Start the API first: dotnet run

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7000/api/v1
@contentType = application/json

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ✅  SEED VERIFICATION
# Run these first to confirm the seed data came through correctly.
# Expected: 200 OK with a list of movies/genres.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [SEED] Verify movies were seeded (should return page 1 with movies)
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies?page=1&pageSize=5
Accept: application/json

###

### [SEED] Verify homepage movies (should return up to 30)
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/homepage
Accept: application/json

###

### [SEED] Verify latest movies (should return 6 entries)
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/latest
Accept: application/json

###

### [SEED] Verify total movie count (should be > 0)
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/count
Accept: application/json

###

### [SEED] Get movie ID 1 — should return 'Freaks Out' with cast/crew/reviews
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/1
Accept: application/json

###

### [SEED] Get movie by slug title
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/by-title/Freaks-Out
Accept: application/json

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🔍  FILTERING & PAGINATION
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Page 1, 12 per page, sorted by title ascending
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies?page=1&pageSize=12&sortBy=title&ascOrDesc=asc
Accept: application/json

###

### Page 1, sorted by rating descending
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies?page=1&pageSize=10&sortBy=ratingImdb&ascOrDesc=desc
Accept: application/json

###

### Filter by title containing "The"
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies?page=1&pageSize=10&title=The
Accept: application/json

###

### Filter movies with IMDb rating > 7.5
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies?page=1&pageSize=10&filterField=RatingImdb&filterValue=7.5&filterOperator=1
Accept: application/json

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🔎  SEARCH
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Full-text search
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/search?searchTerm=war&page=1&pageSize=5
Accept: application/json

###

### Search with rating filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/search?searchTerm=father&minRating=7&maxRating=10&sortBy=ratingImdb&sortDirection=desc
Accept: application/json

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🔗  RELATED MOVIES
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get related movies for movie ID 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/1/related?page=1&pageSize=6
Accept: application/json

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ➕  CREATE
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create a new movie
POST {{baseUrl}}/movies
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Test Movie",
  "photoSrc": "https://example.com/photo.jpg",
  "photoSrcProd": "https://example.com/photo-prod.jpg",
  "trailerSrc": "https://www.youtube.com/embed/dQw4w9WgXcQ",
  "duration": 120,
  "ratingImdb": 7.5,
  "dateAired": "2024-01-15",
  "description": "A great test movie for development purposes.",
  "genreIds": [1],
  "cast": [
    { "actorId": 1, "role": "Hero" }
  ],
  "crew": [
    { "crewId": 1, "role": "Director" }
  ]
}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ✏️  UPDATE
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Update movie (partial — only changed fields required)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/movies/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "description": "Updated description for Freaks Out."
}

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ❌  DELETE
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Delete a movie (use carefully — resets seed state)
# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/movies/999

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🩺  HEALTH CHECK
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Check API + database connectivity
### Expected: 200 Healthy
GET https://localhost:7000/health
Accept: application/json

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ❗  VALIDATION ERRORS (should return 400)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Missing required fields — should return 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/movies
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "X",
  "duration": -5,
  "ratingImdb": 99
}

###

### Search with too-short term — should return 400
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/search?searchTerm=x
Accept: application/json

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 🚫  NOT FOUND (should return 404)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Non-existent movie ID — should return 404 ProblemDetails
GET {{baseUrl}}/movies/99999
Accept: application/json

###
